boundary keeper
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:  1
Definition:a person who keeps watch of stock either within a locality on a property or between two properties.


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
